      "title": "Two dead in drowning incident in Peradeniya",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Two youth aged 17 and 18 have died after drowning in the Nelligala lake, in Peradeniya.",
        "According to the Police, the tragedy had taken place while they were swimming in the lake, and the victims were identified as residents from Yatagalatenne.",
        "According to the drowning prevention report 2020 by Sri Lanka Life Saving 755 drowing related deaths are report each year in the country."
      ],
